data.description: Welcome to this cozy 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in New Smyrna Beach, Florida! Situated in a quiet neighborhood, this block home has everything you need. The living room/dining room area is spacious and perfect for hanging out with friends. Plus, there's a breakfast bar for casual meals.    You'll love the new vinyl flooring, newer appliances, New HVAC (2021), and the hurricane shutters, making this home both stylish and safe. Outside, enjoy the hot tub, enclosed lanai, and fully fenced yard for privacy.  The street ends in a cul-de-sac, so there's hardly any traffic!    The community even has its own park and pavilion! If you ever need to go shopping or hit the beach, it's just a short drive away from grocery stores, parks/trails, down town festivities and the ocean!
